content.rendered:
Directed by Robbie Grewal.

Written by Robbie Grewal. Shreyansh Pandey. Ishraq Shah. Ishraq Shah.

Cast John Abraham(Romeo / Akbar / Walter (RAW)). Mouni Roy(Shraddha). Jackie Shroff(Srikant Rai – RAW Chief). Sikandar Kher(Col Khudabaksh Khan (as Sikander Kher)). Raghuvir Yadav(Muddusar). Rajesh Shringarpure(Prasoon Awasthi). Anil George(Isaq Afridi). Purnendu Bhattacharya(General Zorawar). Suchitra Krishnamoorthi(Rehana Kazmi). Shadaab Khan(Nawab Afridi). Ashish Chhipa(Abhay Prol). Gyanendra Tripathi(Captain Adil). Alka Amin(Waheeda (RAW ‘s Mother)). Shivraj Walvekar(Cabinet Minister Surve). Mohammad Salman Khan(Salman). Sharat Sonu(Robber_2). Vikash Rajput(Vikash Rajput). Jay Bhatt(Rafiq). Tareeq Ahmed Khan(Cop). Mushtaq Kak(Joker).Mudassar Khan. Aashit Chatterjee(General Ghazi). Amit Mishra(Orange Seller). Prahan Rao(Latif Sheikh).Imran Farooq Ganaie. Sushil Dubey(Peon (credit only))

Language Hindi.

Producers Sachin Agarwal. Gary Aranha. Vivek Bhatnagar. Gary Grewal. Chetan Handoo. Ajay Kapoor. Danish Khan. Abdullah Shaikh. Laxmi Singh. Suguna Sundaram. Shilpan Vyas Tinu. Dheeraj Wadhawan. Juspreet Singh Walia. Vanessa Walia.

Production Kyta Productions. NNB Digital Media. VA Film Company.
